<dt>[2]</dt><dd>R. T. Fielding. Maintaining Distributed Hypertext Infostructures: Welcome to MOMspider's Web. Computer Networks and ISDN Systems, 27(2), November 1994, pp. 193-204. (Revision of [7] after special selection by referees.)</dd>
</dl>

